e (financial, legal, operations, HR, IP)</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>6</td>\n          <td>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</td>\n          <td>3.4</td>\n          <td>Amber</td>\n          <td>Financial clarity is adequate but debt and reporting frequencies need improvement.</td>\n          <td>Request access to accounting platform and export financial reports</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>7</td>\n          <td>M4 People</td>\n          <td>3.4</td>\n          <td>Amber</td>\n          <td>People processes are generally robust but position descriptions and HR metrics require attention.</td>\n          <td>Compile full staff list with roles, status, start dates and key-employee flag</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>8</td>\n          <td>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</td>\n          <td>5.0</td>\n          <td>Green</td>\n          <td>Tax and activity statement compliance are fully up to date with no gaps.</td>\n          <td>Verify BAS, IAS and income-tax lodgements have been lodged and paid</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n    <!-- Advisor Report -->\n    <h1>Advisor Report</h1>\n\n    <!-- Section 1 -->\n    <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>\n    <p>\n      Toby Flanders’s premium coffee-bean roasting business demonstrates strong tax compliance (Module 7) and solid financial management (Module 1), underpinned by a cohesive team and sound HR policies (Module 4). The brand and digital assets are in place, but updates are overdue (Module 6). Key gaps are evident in legal documentation and property compliance (Module 2) and in customer, product and revenue quality measures (Module 5). Owner dependency and lack of documented processes (Module 3), absence of a strategic business plan (Module 8) and limited marketing infrastructure further impede sale readiness. Addressing these issues through targeted tasks will enhance buyer confidence and streamline the exit process.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Section 2 -->\n    <h2>2. Module Findings</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: Infrequent meetings with accountant; reporting cadence could be improved.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Weekly review of P&amp;L and balance sheet; no business debt; profitable last year.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: No formalised legal-structure documents; property compliance records missing.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: No pending legal actions; property upgrades not required imminently.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: Lack of documented processes, internal meetings and divisional structure; limited automation and reporting; low technology integration.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Business operates without owner guidance; succession support identified; access to IT support.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M4 People</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: No performance-review schedule; HR metrics not tracked; only some roles documented.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Robust HR policies; cohesive team; clear recruitment needs and retention threat awareness.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: No formal product review or pricing updates; absent sales and marketing strategy; no CRM or customer-service procedures; limited data usage.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Strong product-market fit; high repeat-customer rate; low customer concentration; service-contract coverage.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: Brand assets and style guide updates not tracked; website refresh overdue; premises appeal unassessed.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Established website; style guide in place; high brand consistency rating.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: None identified.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Full compliance; up-to-date BAS and tax lodgements; solid foundation for buyer due diligence.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n        <strong>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: Absence of strategic business plan; no structured data-room or due-diligence checklist.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: International trading plan in place.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <!-- Section 3 -->\n    <h2>3. Module Scores & RAG Ranking</h2>\n    <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n      <thead>\n        <tr>\n          <th>Module</th>\n          <th>Score</th>\n          <th>RAG</th>\n          <th>Rank</th>\n        </tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</td><td>1.0</td><td>Red</td><td>1</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</td><td>1.9</td><td>Red</td><td>2</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</td><td>2.6</td><td>Amber</td><td>3</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</td><td>2.7</td><td>Amber</td><td>4</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</td><td>3.0</td><td>Amber</td><td>5</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</td><td>3.4</td><td>Amber</td><td>6</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>M4 People</td><td>3.4</td><td>Amber</td><td>7</td></tr>\n        <tr><td>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</td><td>5.0</td><td>Green</td><td>8</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n\n    <!-- Section 4 -->\n    <h2>4. Task List by Module</h2>\n\n    <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <!-- TASK_LIBRARY -->\n      <li>Review and collate all corporate governance documents (constitutions, shareholder agreements, trust deeds).</li>\n      <li>Verify and file all property titles, leases and warranties.</li>\n      <li>Engage legal counsel to audit compliance obligations and update registries.</li>\n      <li>Update insurance policies and ensure coverage aligns with asset values.</li>\n      <!-- Bespoke -->\n      <li>Collect all legal-structure documents (constitutions, trusts, shareholder agreements).</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <!-- TASK_LIBRARY -->\n      <li>Conduct a full product and service portfolio review.</li>\n      <li>Benchmark current pricing against key competitors.</li>\n      <li>Develop a CRM implementation plan and select a suitable platform.</li>\n      <li>Design a customer segmentation framework for existing, lapsed and prospect audiences.</li>\n      <li>Establish formal customer service procedures and complaint-handling process.</li>\n      <!-- Bespoke -->\n      <li>Segment customer database into existing, lapsed and prospects.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <!-- TASK_LIBRARY -->\n      <li>Audit all brand assets (logos, marketing collateral, digital templates) for consistency.</li>\n      <li>Review IP registrations, trademarks and renewals.</li>\n      <li>Update the style guide to reflect current brand identity.</li>\n      <li>Inspect the website and social channels for outdated content and broken links.</li>\n      <!-- Bespoke -->\n      <li>Audit brand assets (logos, style guide, website) for consistency.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <!-- TASK_LIBRARY -->\n      <li>Document all critical business processes and procedures in a central manual.</li>\n      <li>Map each owner’s daily and periodic duties for transition.</li>\n      <li>Implement regular internal management and team meeting schedules.</li>\n      <li>Deploy operational reporting dashboards for key performance indicators.</li>\n      <li>Evaluate and adopt automation tools to streamline workflows.</li>\n      <!-- Bespoke -->\n      <li>Document owners’ daily and periodic duties.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <!-- TASK_LIBRARY -->\n      <li>Establish a secure electronic data-room with defined folder structure.</li>\n      <li>Compile due diligence checklist covering financial, legal, operations, HR and IP.</li>\n      <li>Draft an executive summary pack for prospective buyers.</li>\n      <li>Review and organise international trading documentation.</li>\n      <!-- Bespoke -->\n      <li>Create secure data-room folder structure (financial, legal, operations, HR, IP).</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <!-- TASK_LIBRARY -->\n      <li>Schedule fortnightly review meetings with your accountant.</li>\n      <li>Ensure bookkeeping system reconciles monthly and year to date.</li>\n      <li>Produce and circulate monthly management accounts to stakeholders.</li>\n      <li>Implement a rolling 12-month cash flow forecast.</li>\n      <li>Consolidate historical financial statements back three years.</li>\n      <!-- Bespoke -->\n      <li>Request access to accounting platform and export financial reports.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M4 People</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <!-- TASK_LIBRARY -->\n      <li>Update and standardise position descriptions for all staff and contractors.</li>\n      <li>Establish a biannual performance review schedule.</li>\n      <li>Track HR metrics such as absenteeism, turnover and leave balances.</li>\n      <li>Develop a staff recruitment and retention plan aligned to growth needs.</li>\n      <li>Implement formal onboarding and induction procedures.</li>\n      <!-- Bespoke -->\n      <li>Compile full staff list with roles,