 </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>Legal, Compliance & Property (M2)</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: Service-level agreements exist, but property leases, licences and corporate documents need review.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Consolidate all legal-structure documents; review insurance and third-party contracts.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>Customer, Product & Revenue Quality (M5)</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: Infrequent product reviews, outdated pricing, no defined sales process, limited CRM usage and no ROI tracking.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Segment customers, implement CRM effectively and review pricing/marketing strategies.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>Brand, IP & Intangibles (M6)</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: No style guide, website updates infrequent and premises branding not refreshed.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Audit brand assets, develop a style guide and schedule annual updates.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>People (M4)</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: Position descriptions partly in place, no HR policies, infrequent performance reviews and poor team cohesion.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Compile full staff records, introduce HR procedures and performance metrics.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>Due Diligence Preparation (M8)</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: No strategic business plan, partial international trading plan and data-room unstructured.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Create a secure data-room and draft a clear strategic plan with KPIs.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>Owner Dependency & Operations (M3)</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: High owner reliance, undocumented processes, no succession or continuity plan and no regular meetings.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Document daily duties, formalise processes and establish succession backups.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li><strong>Financial Clarity & Reporting (M1)</strong>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Concerns: No bookkeeper, report reviews are monthly but accounting meetings only once a year.</li>\n          <li>Opportunities: Engage bookkeeping support, export financial reports and hold regular review meetings.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>3. Module Scores & RAG Ranking</h2>\n    <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n      <tr>\n        <th>Module</th>\n        <th>Score</th>\n        <th>RAG</th>\n        <th>Rank</th>\n      </tr>\n      <tr><td>Tax, Compliance & Regulatory (M7)</td><td>1.0</td><td>Red</td><td>1</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Legal, Compliance & Property (M2)</td><td>2.3</td><td>Amber</td><td>2</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Customer, Product & Revenue Quality (M5)</td><td>2.3</td><td>Amber</td><td>3</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Brand, IP & Intangibles (M6)</td><td>2.3</td><td>Amber</td><td>4</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>People (M4)</td><td>2.8</td><td>Amber</td><td>5</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Due Diligence Preparation (M8)</td><td>3.0</td><td>Amber</td><td>6</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Owner Dependency & Operations (M3)</td><td>3.1</td><td>Amber</td><td>7</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>Financial Clarity & Reporting (M1)</td><td>3.2</td><td>Amber</td><td>8</td></tr>\n    </table>\n\n    <h2>4. Task List by Module</h2>\n\n    <h3>Tax, Compliance & Regulatory (M7)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Verify BAS, IAS and income-tax lodgements have been lodged and paid.</li>\n      <li>Lodge outstanding BAS, IAS and income-tax returns immediately.</li>\n      <li>Review and maintain all tax compliance records monthly.</li>\n      <li>Schedule regular reviews with your tax advisor to ensure ongoing compliance.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>Legal, Compliance & Property (M2)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Collect all legal-structure documents (constitutions, trusts, shareholder agreements)