 <li>Prepare financial, legal, operational and HR documents for data-room.</li>\n      <li>Maintain and update due diligence materials continuously.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>Owner Dependency & Operations (M3)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Document owners\' daily and periodic duties.</li>\n      <li>Establish a schedule for regular team and divisional meetings.</li>\n      <li>Develop and document all key business processes and procedures.</li>\n      <li>Create a formal succession plan and designate backup roles.</li>\n      <li>Implement an operational reporting framework with regular reviews.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>Financial Clarity & Reporting (M1)</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Request access to accounting platform and export financial reports.</li>\n      <li>Engage a qualified bookkeeper to manage day-to-day finance.</li>\n      <li>Schedule monthly reviews of P&L, balance sheet and cashflow reports.</li>\n      <li>Arrange quarterly meetings with your accountant to discuss and plan.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>5. Additional Bespoke Tasks</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Legal, Compliance & Property (M2): Conduct an audit of any pending legal actions or contingent liabilities.</li>\n      <li>Owner Dependency & Operations (M3): Organise cross-training workshops for key roles.</li>\n      <li>Brand, IP & Intangibles (M6): Carry out a trademark search and register any unprotected IP.</li>\n      <li>Due Diligence Preparation (M8): Set up a governance schedule to update data-room materials monthly.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n  </body>\n</html>','2025-06-17 23:15:43','2025-06-18 01:00:08'),(11,15,12,10,'primary','completed','2025-06-17 23:17:30','2025-06-18 00:34:16',100,'**Critical Issues**  \n- No succession plan despite founders’ imminent retirement, leaving 70% reliance on key owners  \n- Backlog of unfinished work over three days with WIP valued at up to $170K  \n- Low CRM effectiveness (rating 3/10) and absence of marketing ROI tracking  \n- Concentration risk: 33% of revenue 