ry</h2>\n  <p>Manuco’s performance has declined since acquisition, with financial reporting infrequent, critical licences out of date, overdue activity statements and high owner dependency. Operational and HR processes lack consistency, and customer, product and marketing systems are under-utilised. Brand assets are strong online but physical premises need refreshing. A structured programme addressing legal compliance, customer and revenue quality, operational resilience, tax compliance, financial clarity, people management, due diligence readiness and brand consistency will greatly enhance sale readiness.</p>\n\n  <h2>2. Module Findings</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>M1 Financial Clarity &amp; Reporting</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Business performance has worsened since takeover.</li>\n            <li>Financial reviews occur only quarterly.</li>\n            <li>Accountant meetings are annual.</li>\n            <li>Last financial year ended in a loss.</li>\n            <li>Reliance on an overdraft facility.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Owner confident turnaround is possible.</li>\n            <li>Bookkeeping support in place.</li>\n            <li>Debt repayments are being met.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>M2 Legal, Compliance &amp; Property</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Licences are not up to date.</li>\n            <li>No service level agreements with key third parties.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>No current legal actions underway.</li>\n            <li>Properties do not require major upgrades within 12 months.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>M3 Owner Dependency &amp; Operations</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Seventy per cent dependency on owners; business cannot operate without them.</li>\n            <li>Succession plan exists but is not implemented or working.</li>\n            <li>No plan for owner incapacity or departure.</li>\n            <li>Management meetings are ad hoc; operational reports not regularly reviewed.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Board and divisional structure are established.</li>\n            <li>Processes and ERP system are documented and in use.</li>\n            <li>IT support arrangements in place.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>M4 People</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Performance reviews have never been conducted.</li>\n            <li>Position descriptions are incomplete and not recently updated.</li>\n            <li>Under-performing staff and risk of departures.</li>\n            <li>Team cohesion is lacking.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>HR policies and procedures exist.</li>\n            <li>Key-employee framework partially in place.</li>\n            <li>HR data (absenteeism, leave) is measured.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>M5 Customer, Product &amp; Revenue Quality</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Product/service review occurred over a year ago.</li>\n            <li>No formal sales and marketing plan or documented sales process.</li>\n            <li>CRM usage low (2/10) and customer data not captured.</li>\n            <li>High customer concentration; only 10% on contracts.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Prices were updated three months ago.</li>\n            <li>Products remain well suited to the market.</li>\n            <li>Sales and marketing strategy exists.</li>\n            <li>CRM system is in place.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>M6 Brand, IP &amp; Intangibles</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>No style guide.</li>\n            <li>Physical premises require exterior updates.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Website was updated one month ago.</li>\n            <li>Brand consistency rated 10/10 across channels.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>M7 Tax, Compliance &amp; Regulatory</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Activity statements are overdue.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Business tax returns are up to date.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</strong>\n      <ul>\n        <li>Concerns:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Strategic plan last review date is unknown.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n        <li>Opportunities:\n          <ul>\n            <li>Strategic business plan exists.</li>\n            <li>International trading plan is in place.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h2>3. Module Scores &amp; RAG Ranking</h2>\n  <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n      <th>Module</th><th>Score</th><th>RAG</th><th>Rank</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td>M2 Legal, Compliance &amp; Property</td><td>1.0</td><td>Red</td><td>1</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M5 Customer, Product &amp; Revenue Quality</td><td>2.9</td><td>Amber</td><td>2</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M3 Owner Dependency &amp; Operations</td><td>3.0</td><td>Amber</td><td>3</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M7 Tax, Compliance &amp; Regulatory</td><td>3.0</td><td>Amber</td><td>4</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M1