ises eight Sale-Ready modules, with immediate focus on Financial Clarity & Reporting (M1) and Due Diligence Preparation (M8), followed by People (M4), Customer, Product & Revenue Quality (M5), Legal, Compliance & Property (M2), Owner Dependency & Operations (M3), Brand, IP & Intangibles (M6) and ongoing Tax, Compliance & Regulatory maintenance (M7).</p>\n\n    <h1>2. Module Findings</h1>\n    <h2>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concern: Overall loss last year, reliance on overdraft and debt, inability to meet repayments.</li>\n      <li>Concern: Financial reports reviewed only quarterly; accountant meetings once per year.</li>\n      <li>Opportunity: Bookkeeper in place; optimistic about turnaround.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concern: Licences are expired; property requires boardroom paint and roof repairs.</li>\n      <li>Opportunity: No outstanding legal actions; SLAs with third parties exist.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concern: 80 % owner reliance, key processes undocumented, low operational reporting.</li>\n      <li>Opportunity: Board, divisional structure and succession plan exist; ERP system in use.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M4 People</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concern: Under-performing staff, no one-on-one reviews, risk of losing key employees.</li>\n      <li>Opportunity: HR policies in place; HR data (absenteeism, leave) measured.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concern: Product/service review over one year overdue; margins below industry; no sales & marketing plan; weak CRM use.</li>\n      <li>Opportunity: Prices updated three months ago; customers understand offerings; custom solutions differentiate.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concern: No style guide; premises need external facelift.</li>\n      <li>Opportunity: Website current; branding consistency across channels rated 10/10.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Opportunity: BAS, business tax returns and activity statements are up to date.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concern: Strategic business plan review date unknown; no international trading plan.</li>\n      <li>Opportunity: Plan exists; data-room structure can be created swiftly.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h1>3. Task List by Module (Standard Library Tasks)</h1>\n    <h2>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Implement monthly profit & loss review meetings.</li>\n      <li>Develop a rolling 12-month cash flow forecasting model.</li>\n      <li>Automate P&L and balance sheet reporting.</li>\n      <li>Maintain a consolidated debt register.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Ensure all licences and permits are current and reviewed annually.</li>\n      <li>Conduct an annual legal compliance audit.</li>\n      <li>Review property lease and maintenance agreements.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Document core business processes and procedures.</li>\n      <li>Schedule monthly operational performance reviews.</li>\n      <li>Optimise ERP workflows and user training.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M4 People</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Update and standardise position descriptions.</li>\n      <li>Implement bi-annual performance review cycles.</li>\n      <li>Develop a succession and retention plan for key roles.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Establish a quarterly product and service review process.</li>\n      <li>Define and document a formal sales & marketing strategy.</li>\n      <li>Optimise CRM usage and reporting dashboards.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Create a comprehensive brand style guide.</li>\n      <li>Conduct a full brand asset audit.</li>\n      <li>Plan and budget for premises refurbishment.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Maintain up-to-date lodgement and payment schedules for BAS and tax returns.</li>\n      <li>Schedule quarterly compliance reviews.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Set up a secure digital data-room folder structure.</li>\n      <li>Review and update the strategic business plan.</li>\n      <li>Draft an international trading plan framework.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h1>4. Additional Bespoke Tasks</h1>\n    <h2>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Request access to the accounting platform and export historical financial reports.</li>\n      <li>Increase report review frequency from quarterly to monthly.</li>\n      <li>Schedule bi-annual meetings with the external accountant.</li>\n      <li>Review all debt facilities and negotiate improved repayment terms.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Renew all expired licences immediately.</li>\n      <li>Commission contractors to repaint boardroom and repair roofing within three months.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Document daily and periodic duties of each owner.</li>\n      <li>Map and document top-ten critical business processes.</li>\n      <li>Provide advanced ERP training to division managers.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M4 People</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Compile a comprehensive staff register with roles, start dates and key-employee flags.</li>\n      <li>Identify under-performing staff and develop individual improvement plans.</li>\n      <li>Commence one-to-one performance reviews for all team members.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Segment the customer database into