g staff create operational risk\",\"quickWins\":\"Compile full staff list with roles, status, start dates and key-employee flag\"},{\"module\":\"M5\",\"rag\":\"Amber\",\"score\":2.7,\"rank\":3,\"whyPriority\":\"Pricing, product relevance and supplier agreements need optimization\",\"quickWins\":\"Segment customer database into existing, lapsed and prospects\"},{\"module\":\"M2\",\"rag\":\"Amber\",\"score\":3.0,\"rank\":4,\"whyPriority\":\"Legal records and SLA gaps may delay sale due diligence\",\"quickWins\":\"Collect all legal-structure documents (constitutions, trusts, shareholder agreements)\"},{\"module\":\"M6\",\"rag\":\"Amber\",\"score\":3.0,\"rank\":5,\"whyPriority\":\"Brand assets and premises upgrades need alignment for buyer impression\",\"quickWins\":\"Audit brand assets (logos, style guide, website) for consistency\"},{\"module\":\"M3\",\"rag\":\"Amber\",\"score\":3.3,\"rank\":6,\"whyPriority\":\"Owner dependency and process documentation gaps limit transferability\",\"quickWins\":\"Document owners\' daily and periodic duties\"},{\"module\":\"M8\",\"rag\":\"Green\",\"score\":3.7,\"rank\":7,\"whyPriority\":\"Strategic plan and international readiness are well in place\",\"quickWins\":\"Create secure data-room folder structure (financial, legal, operations, HR, IP)\"},{\"module\":\"M7\",\"rag\":\"Green\",\"score\":5.0,\"rank\":8,\"whyPriority\":\"Tax and compliance lodgements are fully up to date\",\"quickWins\":\"Verify BAS, IAS and income-tax lodgements have been lodged and paid\"}]}','<html>\n  <head><title>Advisor Report for Peter Spinda</title></head>\n  <body>\n    <h1>Advisor Report for Peter Spinda</h1>\n\n    <h2>1. Executive summary</h2>\n    <p>\n      The diagnostic reveals strong compliance in tax and regulatory lodgements and a solid strategic plan. Major gaps exist in financial reporting cadence, debt management and owner dependency. HR processes are underdeveloped, with under-performing staff and no regular reviews. Product relevance, pricing and supplier agreements require optimisation. Brand assets and premises need refresh. Addressing these areas with targeted actions will improve transferability, enhance buyer confidence and elevate sale readiness.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>2. Module findings</h2>\n\n    <h3>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concerns:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Inconsistent review of key reports (only quarterly).</li>\n          <li>Annual meeting with accountant insufficient for proactive planning.</li>\n          <li>Last financial year generated a loss.</li>\n          <li>High reliance on external debt and financing facilities.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Opportunities:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Establish regular financial reviews to demonstrate stability.</li>\n          <li>Improve cash-flow forecasts to reassure buyers.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concerns:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Licences are not up to date.</li>\n          <li>No service level agreements with key third-party providers.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Opportunities:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Update licences and compliance records to eliminate due-diligence delays.</li>\n          <li>Formalise SLAs to demonstrate robust vendor governance.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concerns:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Business cannot operate without owner input (70 % dependency).</li>\n          <li>Senior management meetings occur ad hoc rather than on a fixed schedule.</li>\n          <li>Process documentation has not been reviewed recently.</li>\n          <li>Operational reports are not reviewed on a regular basis.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Opportunities:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Document owner duties and standardise handover procedures.</li>\n          <li>Institute a fixed management meeting calendar.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M4 People</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concerns:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Under-performing staff are not managed through performance review.</li>\n          <li>Position descriptions exist only for some team members and are outdated.</li>\n          <li>No regular 1:1 reviews and lack of measurable HR metrics on performance.</li>\n          <li>Threat of losing at least one key staff member in the next six months.</li>\n          <li>Team cohesion and support levels are low.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Opportunities:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Strengthen HR policies and performance management.</li>\n          <li>Improve staff retention through engagement and recognition.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concerns:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Full product/service review not conducted in over a year.</li>\n          <li>Low margins compared to industry standard.</li>\n          <li>Supplier and exclusivity agreements are incomplete.</li>\n          <li>No documented sales and marketing plan or process.</li>\n          <li>CRM under-utilised and marketing ROI not tracked.</li>\n          <li>High customer concentration (top 3 account for 52 % of revenue).</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Opportunities:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Optimise pricing and expand product mix for future relevance.</li>\n          <li>Implement robust CRM analytics and a formal sales process.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Concerns:\n        <ul>\n          <li>No style guide to ensure brand consistency.</li>\n          <li>Physical premises require external appeal upgrades.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Opportunities:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Create a comprehensive brand style guide.</li>\n          <li>Refresh premises and signage to enhance buyer impression.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Strengths:\n        <ul>\n          <li>All Activity Statements and business tax returns are up to date.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Strengths:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Strategic business plan and international trading plan are in place.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Concerns:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Last review date of strategic plan is unknown.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n      <li>Opportunities:\n        <ul>\n          <li>Maintain and date-stamp regular reviews of the strategic plan.</li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>3. Task list by module</h2>\n\n    <h3>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Request access to the accounting platform and export all financial reports.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Collect all legal-structure documents (constitutions, trusts, shareholder agreements).</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Document owners\' daily and periodic duties in standard operating procedures.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M4 People</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Compile a full staff list with roles, status, start dates and key-employee flags.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Segment the customer database into existing customers, lapsed customers and target prospects.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Audit brand assets (logos, style guide, website) for consistency.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Verify that BAS, IAS and income-tax lodgements have been filed and paid.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Create a secure data-room folder structure for financial, legal, operational, HR and IP documents.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>4. Additional bespoke tasks</h2>\n\n    <h3>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Establish monthly management meetings to review profit & loss, balance sheet and cash-flow forecasts.</li>\n      <li>Develop a formal debt-repayment schedule and negotiate improved financing terms.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Update all licences and registrations and file evidence of renewal.</li>\n      <li>Negotiate and finalise SLAs with critical third-party suppliers.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Implement a fixed calendar of senior-management and divisional meetings.</li>\n      <li>Review and update all process and procedure documents, date-stamp each revision.</li>\n      <li>Introduce regular operational report reviews and KPI dashboards.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M4 People</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Draft or update position descriptions for all staff and review annually.</li>\n      <li>Implement quarterly 1:1 performance reviews and establish performance improvement plans.</li>\n      <li>Develop a staff engagement survey and action plan to improve cohesion.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Conduct a full product/service portfolio review and identify future offerings.</li>\n      <li>Negotiate or extend supplier contracts and consider exclusivity where strategic.</li>\n      <li>Create a documented sales process and train the team on its use.</li>\n      <li>Implement CRM analytics to track customer behaviour and marketing ROI.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Develop and publish a brand style guide covering logos, colours and tone of voice.</l