m BAS and tax lodgements are current\"},{\"module\":\"M2\",\"rag\":\"Green\",\"score\":5.0,\"rank\":6,\"whyPriority\":\"Legal and property compliance is up to date\",\"quickWins\":\"Gather and review supplier and customer contracts\"},{\"module\":\"M7\",\"rag\":\"Green\",\"score\":5.0,\"rank\":7,\"whyPriority\":\"Tax lodgements are current\",\"quickWins\":\"Download ATO account extract to verify balances\"},{\"module\":\"M8\",\"rag\":\"Green\",\"score\":5.0,\"rank\":8,\"whyPriority\":\"Strategic plan in place and recently reviewed\",\"quickWins\":\"Create secure data-room folder structure\"}]}','<html>\n<body>\n<h2>Roadmap Table</h2>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Rank</th>\n<th>Module</th>\n<th>Score</th>\n<th>RAG</th>\n<th>Why Priority</th>\n<th>Quick Wins</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</td>\n<td>2.8</td>\n<td>Amber</td>\n<td>Website style guide missing and premises need updating</td>\n<td>Audit and refresh your website and premises branding immediately</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>M4 People</td>\n<td>3.2</td>\n<td>Amber</td>\n<td>HR policies and performance review cadence need improvement</td>\n<td>Implement quarterly one-to-one performance reviews this month</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</td>\n<td>3.6</td>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>Owner dependency documentation and SOPs are lacking</td>\n<td>Document owners’ daily duties and critical processes now</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</td>\n<td>4.3</td>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>Marketing ROI tracking is inconsistent</td>\n<td>Set up simple ROI tracking for your next campaign</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</td>\n<td>5.0</td>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>Financial reporting is robust</td>\n<td>Confirm BAS and tax lodgements are current</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</td>\n<td>5.0</td>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>Legal and property compliance is up to date</td>\n<td>Gather and review supplier and customer contracts</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</td>\n<td>5.0</td>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>Tax lodgements are current</td>\n<td>Download ATO account extract to verify balances</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</td>\n<td>5.0</td>\n<td>Green</td>\n<td>Strategic plan in place and recently reviewed</td>\n<td>Create secure data-room folder structure</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Advisor Report</h2>\n\n<h3>1. Executive summary</h3>\n<p>Zohaib Aamer’s business demonstrates strong financial controls, compliance and operational performance, underpinned by effective CRM and marketing processes. To maximise buyer appeal and streamline due diligence, focus on strengthening HR frameworks, documenting owner-dependent processes and enhancing brand presentation across digital assets and the premises.</p>\n\n<h3>2. Module findings</h3>\n\n<h4>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Concern: Absence of a formal website style guide</li>\n<li>Concern: Premises branding and appearance require modernisation</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Refresh digital and physical brand assets to boost buyer confidence</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M4 People</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Concern: HR policies lack a structured framework</li>\n<li>Concern: No regular cadence for performance reviews</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Implement consistent review cycles to reinforce performance management</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Concern: Critical processes are not documented</li>\n<li>Concern: High dependency on owner for daily operations</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Develop SOPs to reduce single-person risk</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Concern: Inconsistent tracking of marketing ROI</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Establish clear ROI metrics to optimise spend</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Strength: Financial reporting is thorough and aligned with standards</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Maintain current BAS and tax lodgements</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Strength: Legal and property compliance fully up to date</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Centralise contract register for efficient access</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Strength: All tax lodgements are current</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Regularly reconcile ATO extracts to pre-empt issues</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Strength: Strategic plan exists and is recently reviewed</li>\n<li>Opportunity: Establish a structured virtual data-room</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>3. Task list by module</h3>\n\n<h4>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Develop a comprehensive brand style guide</li>\n<li>Catalogue all intangible assets and IP rights</li>\n<li>Audit and refresh website branding and design</li>\n<li>Update premises signage, décor and branding elements</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M4 People</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Review and update the HR policy manual in line with best practice</li>\n<li>Establish a formal performance management framework</li>\n<li>Implement quarterly one-to-one performance reviews this month</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Document key personnel responsibilities and reporting lines</li>\n<li>Develop standard operating procedures for critical business functions</li>\n<li>Document owners’ daily duties and critical processes now</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Implement a marketing performance dashboard</li>\n<li>Define clear ROI metrics for all campaigns</li>\n<li>Set up simple ROI tracking for your next campaign</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Prepare up-to-date management accounts and cash-flow forecasts</li>\n<li>Ensure timely lodgement of BAS and tax returns</li>\n<li>Confirm BAS and tax lodgements are current</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Maintain a central register of supplier and customer contracts</li>\n<li>Review all compliance certificates and licences</li>\n<li>Gather and review supplier and customer contracts</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Reconcile ATO account extracts on a monthly basis</li>\n<li>Establish an annual schedule for tax and regulatory lodgements</li>\n<li>Download ATO account extract to verify balances</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compile a comprehensive due diligence documentation checklist</li>\n<li>Establish a secure virtual data-room with clear folder structure</li>\n<li>Create secure data-room folder structure</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>4. Additional bespoke tasks</h3>\n\n<h4>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Register domain variations to protect brand identity</li>\n<li>Conduct a trademark review and renew registrations</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M4 People</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Develop a succession plan for key roles</li>\n<li>Conduct an employee engagement survey and action plan</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Identify and train backups for owner-dependent functions</li>\n<li>Schedule cross-training sessions for critical roles</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Review customer feedback processes for product improvement</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Implement a rolling three-year financial forecast</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Set a biannual contract compliance audit schedule</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Engage a tax advisor for advanced structuring advice</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Test access permissions for the data-room with third-party users</li>\n</ul>\n</body>\n</html>','2025-09-11 11:06:2