IP &amp; Intangibles</td>\n      <td>Green</td>\n      <td>3.8</td>\n      <td>7</td>\n      <td>Brand and website consistency generally sound</td>\n      <td>Audit brand assets (logos, style guide, website) for consistency</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>M7 Tax, Compliance &amp; Regulatory</td>\n      <td>Green</td>\n      <td>5.0</td>\n      <td>8</td>\n      <td>Tax lodgements up to date with no issues</td>\n      <td>Verify BAS, IAS and income-tax lodgements have been lodged and paid</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2>Advisor Report</h2>\n\n  <h3>1. Executive summary</h3>\n  <p>\n    Stepping Into Your Power Pty Ltd, led by Laura McIntosh, demonstrates strong compliance in tax (M7) and solid brand integrity (M6). However, critical deficiencies in due diligence preparation (M8), people and HR policies (M4), and owner dependency and operations (M3) pose significant sale-readiness risks. Amber-rated modules—customer/product quality (M5), legal compliance (M2) and financial reporting (M1)—also require targeted enhancements. Immediate focus on red modules will establish robust foundations, reduce risk and position the business for scalable growth and a successful exit.\n  </p>\n\n  <h3>2. Module findings</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>M8 Due Diligence Preparation:</strong> No strategic business plan or centralised data room; opportunity to implement a secure folder structure for all due diligence documents.</li>\n    <li><strong>M4 People:</strong> Absence of formal HR policies, employee handbook and performance management; opportunity to compile a complete staff register and establish key-employee designations.</li>\n    <li><strong>M3 Owner Dependency &amp; Operations:</strong> High reliance on the director with no documented processes; opportunity to map and document owner duties and standard operating procedures.</li>\n    <li><strong>M5 Customer, Product &amp; Revenue Quality:</strong> Limited segmentation of customer base and inconsistent marketing strategies; opportunity to segment customers and refine the revenue model.</li>\n    <li><strong>M2 Legal, Compliance &amp; Property:</strong> Partial documentation of corporate structure and contracts; opportunity to gather and standardise all legal-structure documents.</li>\n    <li><strong>M1 Financial Clarity &amp; Reporting:</strong> Basic financials exist but lack depth in reporting and analysis; opportunity to extract full financial reports and perform variance analysis.</li>\n    <li><strong>M6 Brand, IP &amp; Intangibles:</strong> Strong brand assets but no formal IP register; opportunity to audit and document all intangible assets.</li>\n    <li><strong>M7 Tax, Compliance &amp; Regulatory:</strong> Fully current lodgements; opportunity to verify and document all tax payments and compliance reports.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>3. Module scores &amp; RAG ranking</h3>\n  <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n      <th>Module</th>\n      <th>Score</th>\n      <th>RAG</th>\n      <th>Rank</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</td><td>1.0</td><td>Red</td><td>1</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M4 People</td><td>1.4</td><td>Red</td><td>2</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M3 Owner Dependency &amp; Operations</td><td>1.8</td><td>Red</td><td>3</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M5 Customer, Product &amp; Revenue Quality</td><td>2.1</td><td>Amber</td><td>4</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M2 Legal, Compliance &amp; Property</td><td>3.0</td><td>Amber</td><td>5</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M1 Financial Clarity &amp; Reporting</td><td>3.2</td><td>Amber</td><td>6</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M6 Brand, IP &amp; Intangibles</td><td>3.8</td><td>Green</td><td>7</td></tr>\n    <tr><td>M7 Tax, Compliance &amp; Regulatory</td><td>5.0</td><td>Green</td><td>8</td></tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <h3>4. Task list by module</h3>\n\n  <h4>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Reconcile all accounts payable and receivable.</li>\n    <li>Perform variance analysis on monthly profit &amp; loss against budget.</li>\n    <li>Request access to accounting platform and export financial reports.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Review current insurance policies for adequacy.</li>\n    <li>Update and standardise corporate structure documentation.</li>\n    <li>Collect all legal-structure documents (constitutions, trusts, shareholder agreements).</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>M3 Owner Dependency &amp; Operations</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Develop documented standard operating procedures for all key processes.</li>\n    <li>Identify and assign process owners for critical functions.</li>\n    <li>Document owners\' daily and periodic duties.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>M4 People</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Create and distribute an employee handbook.</li>\n    <li>Establish a regular performance review schedule.</li>\n    <li>Compile full staff list with roles, status, start dates and key-employee flag.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>M5 Customer, Product &amp; Revenue Quality</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Review customer feedback and implement an improvement plan.</li>\n    <li>Analyse sales pipeline conversion rates.</li>\n    <li>Segment customer database into existing, lapsed and prospects.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>M6 Brand, IP &amp; Intangibles</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Register all intellectual property assets.</li>\n    <li>Implement brand guidelines across all marketing materials.</li>\n    <li>Audit brand assets (logos, style guide, website) for consistency.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>M7 Tax, Compliance &amp; Regulatory</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Conduct a comprehensive tax compliance audit.</li>\n    <li>Review superannuation obligations and payments.</li>\n    <li>Verify BAS, IAS and income-tax lodgements have been lodged and paid.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h4>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Draft a comprehensive due diligence questionnaire for buyers.</li>\n    <li>Establish a centralised data-room with controlled access.</li>\n    <li>Create secure data-room folder structure (financial, legal, operations, HR, IP).</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>5. Additional bespoke tasks</h3>\n  <p>No additional bespoke tasks identified at this stage.</p>\n</body>\n</html>','red','diagnostic','2025-05-26 21:48:14','2025-05-26 21:48:14'),(2,1,NULL,'Diagnostic Advice',1,0,'<html>\n  <body>\n    <h1>Advisor Report for James Ussery</h1>\n\n    <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>\n    <p>\n      The diagnostic highlights critical gaps in legal, compliance and due-diligence readiness, as well as the absence of a strategic business and international trading plan. Financial reporting and bookkeeping practices require strengthening alongside brand and intangible asset management. Operational dependency on the owners, incomplete process documentation and limited HR policies represent further mid-level risks. Customer and product reviews, pricing and marketing data processes also need attention. Tax lodgements and IT support are well maintained and represent lower-priority items.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>2. Module Findings</h2>\n\n    <h3>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Reports are reviewed only quarterly and there is no bookkeeper in place.</li>\n      <li>Meetings with the accountant occur quarterly, limiting timely insight.</li>\n      <li>The business generated a profit last year, demonstrating underlying financial health.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>No service level agreements exist with third parties.</li>\n      <li>Legal-structure documentation (constitutions, trust deeds, shareholder agreements) is incomplete.</li>\n      <li>No property upgrade requirements in the next 12 months, reducing capital outlay risk.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>The business cannot operate without owner guidance and lacks documented processes.</li>\n      <li>Management and operational reports are ad hoc or non-existent.</li>\n      <li>Divisional structure exists with some team meetings; technology systems and IT support are strong.</li>\n      <li>No succession or continuity plan is in place, increasing key-person risk.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M4 People</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Position descriptions exist only for some team members and HR policies are absent.</li>\n      <li>1:1 performance reviews are never conducted.</li>\n      <li>Staff cohesion is strong and recruitment needs are known, reducing turnover risk.</li>\n      <li>No HR data (absenteeism, leave) is measured to guide workforce management.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Products and services have never undergone a full review and prices were last updated over a year ago.</li>\n      <li>Margins are only at industry average and customer segmentation is lacking.</li>\n      <li>Sales and marketing strategy exists but lacks a formal plan and ROI tracking.</li>\n      <li>Sales process is clear, with products remaining relevant to market needs.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Website exists but has not been updated in over two years.</li>\n      <li>No style guide is in place and physical premises lack branding refresh plans.</li>\n      <li>Brand assets have not been audited for consistency across channels.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>All Activity Statements and tax returns are up to date.</li>\n      <li>Minimal attention required; compliance framework is well maintained.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>No strategic business plan or international trading plan exists.</li>\n      <li>Data-room structures and due-diligence documentation frameworks are not set up.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>3. Module Scores & RAG Ranking</h2>\n    <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n      <tr>\n        <th>Module</th>\n        <th>Score</th>\n        <th>RAG</th>\n        <th>Rank</th>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</td>\n        <td>1.0</td>\n        <td style=\"color:red\">Red</td>\n        <td>1</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</td>\n        <td>1.0</td>\n        <td style=\"color:red\">Red</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</td>\n        <td>2.0</td>\n        <td style=\"color:orange\">Amber</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</td>\n        <td>2.3</td>\n        <td style=\"color:orange\">Amber</td>\n        <td>4</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</td>\n        <td>2.6</td>\n        <td style=\"color:orange\">Amber</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M4 People</td>\n        <td>2.6</td>\n        <td style=\"color:orange\">Amber</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</td>\n        <td>2.8</td>\n        <td style=\"color:orange\">Amber</td>\n        <td>7</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</td>\n        <td>5.0</td>\n        <td style=\"color:green\">Green</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n\n    <h2>4. Task List by Module</h2>\n\n    <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Collect all legal-structure documents (constitutions, trust deeds, shareholder agreements).</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Create a secure data-room folder structure covering financials, legal, operations, HR and IP.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Request access to the accounting platform and export current financial reports.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Audit brand assets (logos, style guide, website) to ensure consistency.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Document owners’ daily and periodic duties in a central operations manual.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M4 People</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Compile a full staff list with roles, status, start dates and key-employee flag.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Segment the customer database into existing, lapsed and prospective clients.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Verify BAS, IAS and income-tax lodgements have been filed and paid.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h2>5. Additional Bespoke Tasks</h2>\n\n    <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance & Property</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Negotiate and formalise service level agreements with all key third-party providers.</li>\n      <li>Review lease and property documentation for compliance with current regulations.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Draft a comprehensive strategic business plan with clear objectives and milestones.</li>\n      <li>Develop an international trading plan including market entry strategies and compliance checklists.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M1 Financial Clarity & Reporting</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Engage a qualified bookkeeper to maintain up-to-date ledgers and reconcile accounts monthly.</li>\n      <li>Schedule monthly meetings with the accountant to review P&L, cash flow and key KPIs.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M6 Brand, IP & Intangibles</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Create and implement a corporate style guide covering visual identity and tone of voice.</li>\n      <li>Plan and execute a brand refresh for physical premises, including signage and décor updates.</li>\n      <li>Update website content and design to reflect current positioning and SEO best practices.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M3 Owner Dependency & Operations</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Fully document all core business processes and procedures for handover and training.</li>\n      <li>Establish regular management and team meeting cadences with predefined agendas.</li>\n      <li>Implement a formal succession and continuity plan for key-person risk mitigation.</li>\n      <li>Ensure integration between technology systems to automate workflows and reporting.</li>\n      <li>Schedule weekly operational-report reviews to monitor performance and bottlenecks.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M4 People</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Develop and roll out HR policies and procedures covering recruitment, induction and exits.</li>\n      <li>Institute quarterly 1:1 performance reviews with documented objectives and feedback.</li>\n      <li>Begin tracking HR metrics (absenteeism, leave utilisation, turnover) in an HR dashboard.</li>\n      <li>Review and update all position descriptions annually to align with business needs.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M5 Customer, Product & Revenue Quality</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Conduct a full product and service portfolio review to identify high-value offerings.</li>\n      <li>Update pricing models to enhance margins while remaining competitive.</li>\n      <li>Develop a formal sales and marketing plan with budgets, channels and ROI targets.</li>\n      <li>Implement tools to track and report on marketing expenditure and sales conversion rates.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <h3>M7 Tax, Compliance & Regulatory</h3>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Maintain a compliance calendar for all tax, regulatory and reporting deadlines.</li>\n      <li>Conduct an annual review of tax-effective structures and entitlements.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>','red','diagnostic','2025-05-26 21:49:32','2025-05-26 21:49:32'),(3,3,NULL,'Diagnostic Advice',1,0,'<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <title>Sale-Ready Prioritisation Roadmap and Advisor Report</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Sale-Ready Prioritisation Roadmap</h1>\n  <table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Module</th>\n        <th>Score</th>\n        <th>RAG</th>\n        <th>Rank</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M2 Legal, Compliance &amp; Property</td>\n        <td>1.0</td>\n        <td>Red</td>\n        <td>1</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</td>\n        <td>2.3</td>\n        <td>Amber</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M5 Customer, Product &amp; Revenue Quality</td>\n        <td>2.8</td>\n        <td>Amber</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M1 Financial Clarity &amp; Reporting</td>\n        <td>3.2</td>\n        <td>Amber</td>\n        <td>4</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M4 People</td>\n        <td>3.5</td>\n        <td>Green</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M3 Owner Dependency &amp; Operations</td>\n        <td>3.6</td>\n        <td>Green</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M6 Brand, IP &amp; Intangibles</td>\n        <td>4.0</td>\n        <td>Green</td>\n        <td>7</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>M7 Tax, Compliance &amp; Regulatory</td>\n        <td>5.0</td>\n        <td>Green</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n  <h1>Advisor Report</h1>\n\n  <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>\n  <p>\n    The diagnostic reveals critical gaps in licensing, property compliance and strategic planning, requiring immediate attention under Legal, Compliance &amp; Property (M2) and Due Diligence Preparation (M8). Finance reporting (M1) and marketing execution (M5) also demand targeted improvements. Operational maturity (M3) and HR functions (M4) show moderate performance, while Brand &amp; IP (M6) and Tax compliance (M7) are solid foundations to maintain. Prioritise legal compliance and strategic roadmap development to de-risk the exit process and enhance sale readiness.\n  </p>\n\n  <h2>2. Module Findings</h2>\n\n  <h3>M2 Legal, Compliance &amp; Property</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Concerns:</strong> Licences are not up to date; property upgrade requirements are unresolved.</li>\n    <li><strong>Opportunities:</strong> Renew and standardise licences; schedule necessary property works to mitigate buyer concerns.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>M8 Due Diligence Preparation</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Concerns:</strong> Strategic plan is outdated and lacks record of last review; no international trading plan.</li>\n    <li><strong>Opportunities:</strong> Refresh the strategic roadmap; develop an international trading framework to demonstrate growth potential.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>M5 Customer, Product &amp; Revenue Quality</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Concerns:</strong> Product and service reviews are over one year old; no sales process or marketing plan; high customer concentration risk.</li>\n    <li><strong>Opportunities:</strong> Conduct a full product/service audit; implement a structured sales and marketing strategy; diversify customer base.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>M1 Financial Clarity &amp; Reporting</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Concerns:</strong> Financial performance has declined; profit and loss and other reports are reviewed only quarterly; management meetings with the accountant occur annually.</li>\n    <li><strong>Opportunities:</strong> Increase the frequency of financial reviews to monthly; establish a regular meeting cadence with financial advisors.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>M4 People</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Concerns:</strong> Position descriptions are incomplete and outdated; no formal performance review process; issues with team cohesion.</li>\n    <li><strong>Opportunities:</strong> Update and standardise position descriptions; implement quarterly performance reviews; improve staff engagement.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>M3 Owner Dependency &amp; Operations</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Concerns:</st