itical CEO duties and nominate two deputies. 3. Schedule weekly 2-hour shadowing sessions where deputies perform selected CEO tasks under supervision. 4. Create a handover checklist and capture detailed notes during each session. 5. After two sessions, evaluate progress and update the plan to close any remaining gaps.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(518,20,NULL,NULL,0,'operations','Establish Weekly WIP Backlog Review Meetings','1. Schedule a recurring 30-minute stand-up every Monday morning. 2. Build a shared WIP tracker highlighting tasks >3 days old and valued at over US$10,000. 3. Assign ownership and realistic deadlines for each overdue item. 4. Escalate any high-risk deliverables to the management team for rapid resolution. 5. Review progress in the next meeting, close completed tasks, and refine the process for efficiency.',NULL,0,'critical',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(519,20,NULL,NULL,0,'customers','Configure CRM for Automated ROI Tracking','1. Audit current CRM fields and remove redundant entries. 2. Define campaign codes for every marketing initiative. 3. Add custom fields to capture budget, spend and lead source. 4. Create automated reports linking campaign spend to conversion and revenue. 5. Train sales and marketing teams on accurate data entry; schedule a follow-up in two weeks to troubleshoot issues.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(520,20,NULL,NULL,0,'financial','Build Real-Time Marketing Analytics Dashboard','1. Agree on key metrics: cost per lead, conversion rate, ROI. 2. Connect CRM and Google Analytics to a BI tool (Power BI or Data Studio). 3. Design and publish a dashboard displaying campaign performance and ROI. 4. Validate data accuracy using last quarter’s campaign results. 5. Conduct a 1-hour training session for stakeholders on reading and interpreting dashboard insights.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(521,20,NULL,NULL,0,'human-resources','Develop Underperformer Coaching and Remediation Plans','1. List all staff flagged as underperforming and outline specific performance gaps. 2. Hold one-on-one meetings to discuss issues and set improvement targets. 3. Create individual Performance Improvement Plans (PIPs) with clear objectives, actions, and timelines. 4. Assign mentors and schedule bi-weekly check-ins. 5. After four weeks, review progress and decide on next steps (additional training, role change, or further coaching).',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(522,20,NULL,NULL,0,'human-resources','Launch Employee Engagement and Upskilling Programme','1. Distribute a 5-minute survey to all staff to identify engagement drivers and skill gaps. 2. Develop a 6-month training calendar covering priority technical and soft skills. 3. Allocate budgets for internal and external trainers; secure approval. 4. Introduce a monthly recognition scheme (e.g., peer-nominated award). 5. Review engagement survey results quarterly and adjust the programme based on feedback.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(523,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Plan and Execute Premises Refresh Project','1. Conduct a walk-through audit of reception, meeting rooms and communal areas to list cosmetic and functional improvements. 2. Obtain at least three competitive quotes for painting, signage and minor furniture updates. 3. Finalise scope and budget; schedule the works during off-peak hours. 4. Communicate timelines to staff and arrange temporary workspace if needed. 5. Oversee quality checks on completion and gather feedback from employees and clients.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(524,20,NULL,NULL,0,'competitive-forces','Update Competitor Benchmarking Report','1. Collect public data on offerings, pricing and marketing tactics of Cogent, Devsinc and Techlogix. 2. Analyze their strengths and weaknesses against your AI services. 3. Identify three unique differentiators you can highlight in your positioning. 4. Present findings and recommended strategic shifts to the leadership team. 5. Schedule quarterly updates to keep the report current.',NULL,0,'low',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(525,20,NULL,NULL,0,'diagnostic','Audit Single-Point Dependencies and Mitigation Measures','1. List all critical tasks currently performed exclusively by the CEO. 2. Identify at least two backup personnel for each task and document required access levels. 3. Develop step-by-step guides for each task and store in the shared knowledge base. 4. Hold cross-training sessions over the next two weeks where backups execute each task. 5. Conduct a practical assessment to verify readiness and adjust training as needed.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(526,20,NULL,NULL,0,'tax','Review Tax Compliance and Forecast','1. Confirm that all Activity Statements and tax returns remain up-to-date. 2. Meet with your accountant to project tax liabilities for the coming quarter. 3. Update the cash-flow forecast to include expected tax payments. 4. Set calendar reminders one month before each filing deadline. 5. Document any changes to tax assumptions and share with the finance team.',NULL,0,'low',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:26:01','2025-09-11 12:26:01'),(527,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Conduct a Comprehensive Business Health Audit','1. Gather key financial statements (profit & loss, balance sheet, cash flow) for the past 12 months.\n2. Compile operational metrics (production volumes, sales figures, inventory levels) from internal systems.\n3. Collect customer data (satisfaction surveys, Net Promoter Score, churn rates).\n4. Analyze each dataset to identify trends, strengths, and risk areas.\n5. Summarize findings in a one-page report highlighting top three areas for improvement.',NULL,0,'critical',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:27:11','2025-09-11 12:27:11'),(528,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Review and Update Your Business Plan','1. Revisit your company’s mission, vision, and value proposition.\n2. Compare current performance against original goals and market assumptions.\n3. Identify changes in industry trends or customer needs that require plan adjustments.\n4. Rewrite strategic objectives using the SMART framework (Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, Time-bound).\n5. Distribute the updated plan to key stakeholders and schedule a review meeting.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:27:11','2025-09-11 12:27:11'),(529,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Perform a 30-Day Cash Flow Forecast','1. Extract historical cash inflows and outflows from accounting software for the last six months.\n2. Project receivables based on outstanding invoices and expected payment dates.\n3. Estimate upcoming expenses (payroll, supplier payments, rent, utilities).\n4. Build a day-by-day cash flow spreadsheet for the next 30 days.\n5. Identify potential shortfalls and plan financing or cost-control measures to bridge gaps.',NULL,0,'critical',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:27:11','2025-09-11 12:27:11'),(530,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Develop a 30-Day Marketing Campaign','1. Define a clear campaign objective (lead generation, brand awareness, promotion).\n2. Segment your target audience and select appropriate channels (email, social media, paid ads).\n3. Create a content calendar with daily/weekly themes, ad copy, and creative assets.\n4. Allocate budget by channel and set performance metrics (CPC, click-through rate, conversion rate).\n5. Launch the campaign, monitor performance daily, and adjust tactics based on real-time results.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:27:11','2025-09-11 12:27:11'),(531,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Implement a Customer Feedback Process','1. Design a short survey (5–7 questions) focusing on product/service experience and improvement areas.\n2. Choose distribution channels (email, website pop-up, in-person) and schedule dispatch timing.\n3. Send to a representative sample of recent customers and set a deadline for responses.\n4. Aggregate results in a dashboard, categorize feedback by theme, and calculate key scores.\n5. Hold a team workshop to brainstorm solutions for the top three feedback issues.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:27:11','2025-09-11 12:27:11'),(532,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Optimize Core Operational Workflows','1. Map existing workflows for order fulfillment, customer service, or production.\n2. Identify bottlenecks or manual handoffs that cause delays or errors.\n3. Brainstorm and document at least two process improvement ideas for each bottleneck.\n4. Pilot the top improvement in a small segment or team for one week.\n5. Evaluate pilot results, refine the process, and roll out improvements company-wide.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:27:11','2025-09-11 12:27:11'),(533,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Clarify Team Roles and Responsibilities','1. Create or update an org chart with current roles and reporting lines.\n2. Write clear role descriptions highlighting key responsibilities and performance metrics.\n3. Schedule one-on-one meetings with each team member to review expectations and answer questions.\n4. Set individual 30-day goals aligned with business priorities.\n5. Convene a team meeting to share updated roles, celebrate clarity, and address any overlap or gaps.',NULL,0,'low',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:27:11','2025-09-11 12:27:11'),(534,20,NULL,NULL,0,'human-resources','Implement and Test Succession Plan','Zohaib Aamer to schedule a board meeting within 5 days; 1) Review current succession plan document and assign a second-in-command; 2) Define interim authority levels and sign off by all directors; 3) Develop a 48-hour emergency handover checklist; 4) Conduct a simulated CEO absence scenario with the leadership team; 5) Gather feedback, refine steps and reconvene to finalize plan updates.',NULL,0,'critical',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(535,20,NULL,NULL,0,'operations','Document and Standardize Core Processes','Zohaib Aamer to appoint a process owner and: 1) Identify top five workflows (sales onboarding, project intake, billing, support escalation, quality assurance); 2) Map each workflow step using simple flowcharts or templates; 3) Validate maps in a workshop with stakeholders; 4) Publish finalized procedure documents in a shared repository; 5) Train staff on new standards and set due date for full adoption.',NULL,0,'critical',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(536,20,NULL,NULL,0,'operations','Optimize WIP Management and Clear $1M Backlog','Zohaib Aamer to lead an operations review: 1) Run a 30-day WIP aging report; 2) Identify bottlenecks by team and project stage; 3) Reallocate resources or shift priorities to high-value jobs; 4) Introduce a weekly WIP clearance meeting; 5) Track daily completion rates and adjust assignments to clear backlog within 4 weeks.',NULL,0,'critical',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(537,20,NULL,NULL,0,'customers','Enhance CRM Capabilities and Implement ROI Tracking','Zohaib Aamer to coordinate with sales and IT: 1) Audit current CRM fields and workflows; 2) Define key ROI metrics (cost per lead, deal cycle time, conversion rate); 3) Configure CRM dashboards for real-time ROI tracking; 4) Train team on entering campaign spend and outcome data; 5) Schedule weekly CRM review in sales meeting.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(538,20,NULL,NULL,0,'customers','Develop Customer Diversification Strategy','Zohaib Aamer to drive a marketing and sales workshop: 1) Analyze top three clients and revenue concentration risks; 2) Identify three new target segments or geographies; 3) Create value propositions and outreach templates; 4) Assign responsibility and timeline for first pilot outreach; 5) Review progress in bi-weekly sales meetings.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(539,20,NULL,NULL,0,'general','Plan and Execute Premises Upgrade','Zohaib Aamer to form a small task force: 1) Conduct a walk-through of office to list required improvements (paint, signage, workstations); 2) Obtain three quotes from contractors; 3) Draft scope, timeline and budget; 4) Approve vendor and schedule work during low-traffic hours; 5) Communicate schedule and safety measures to staff.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(540,20,NULL,NULL,0,'operations','Automate Key Workflow Steps Using Slack and Managition','Zohaib Aamer to collaborate with IT: 1) Identify repetitive manual tasks in Slack/Managition (eg. attendance check, task reminders); 2) Configure or build simple bots or integrations; 3) Test in a pilot group; 4) Document automation steps; 5) Roll out company-wide and train users.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(541,20,NULL,NULL,0,'human-resources','Develop Staff Recruitment and Retention Plan','Zohaib Aamer to partner with HR lead: 1) Audit current headcount vs. forecast needs; 2) Create role briefs for urgent hires; 3) Define interview, induction and probation processes; 4) Introduce monthly check-ins and mentorship pairs; 5) Set targets for employee satisfaction and turnover rates.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(542,20,NULL,NULL,0,'financial','Introduce Marketing ROI Tracking Framework','Zohaib Aamer to work with marketing: 1) List all channels and associated spend; 2) Assign unique tracking codes or UTM parameters; 3) Set up automated reports pulling data into a central dashboard; 4) Review performance weekly and reallocate budget to top-performing channels; 5) Document process for ongoing updates.',NULL,0,'high',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(543,20,NULL,NULL,0,'financial','Audit and Enhance Weekly Financial Review Process','Zohaib Aamer to meet accountant and finance team: 1) Validate current bank statement, cash-flow and budget review templates; 2) Introduce variance analysis vs. forecast; 3) Add key ratio tracking (working capital days, WIP turnover); 4) Implement action-item log from each review; 5) Ensure corrective actions are assigned and followed up.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(544,20,NULL,NULL,0,'competitive-forces','Refresh Competitive Analysis and Technology Advantage','Zohaib Aamer to conduct a rapid competitor scan: 1) Update profiles of Cogent, Devsinc, Techlogix; 2) Map features, pricing and service gaps; 3) Highlight unique strengths of your Slack + Managition stack; 4) Identify two automation or integration enhancements to differentiate; 5) Brief sales and marketing teams on revised positioning.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(545,20,NULL,NULL,0,'diagnostic','Set and Review Key Operational KPIs','Zohaib Aamer to define and implement KPI dashboard: 1) Select metrics (absenteeism, workload utilization, WIP aging); 2) Assign data sources and reporting frequency; 3) Build simple dashboard in existing tools; 4) Train operations managers to review weekly; 5) Hold first KPI review meeting with action-item tracking.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(546,20,NULL,NULL,0,'legal-licensing','Confirm Legal and Licensing Status','Zohaib Aamer to liaise with company secretary: 1) Review any local regulations or industry codes; 2) Confirm no licences are required; 3) Document confirmation in compliance folder; 4) Set annual reminder to re-check status; 5) Update board at next meeting.',NULL,0,'low',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(547,20,NULL,NULL,0,'tax','Schedule Tax Compliance and Upcoming Filings','Zohaib Aamer to meet internal bookkeeper: 1) List upcoming tax due dates; 2) Confirm all activity statements and business returns are up to date; 3) Ensure provision accruals for next quarter; 4) File any missing returns within 14 days; 5) Set calendar reminders for future lodgments.',NULL,0,'low',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20'),(548,20,NULL,NULL,0,'due-diligence','Prepare Due Diligence Documentation Pack','Zohaib Aamer to coordinate data gathering: 1) Compile latest financial statements, process docs, succession plan, leases, contracts; 2) Organise into a secure shared folder with access controls; 3) Create an index and summary memo; 4) Review pack with accountant and legal counsel; 5) Finalise for potential investor or buyer review.',NULL,0,'medium',0,'needs-action',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-09-11 12:28:20','2025-09-11 12:28:20');
